spec_data.Name: mono-extras
spec_data.Description:
This package provides the library and application to run services
and daemons with Mono. It also includes stubs for the following
assemblies: Microsoft.Vsa,
System.Configuration.Install, System.Management, System.Messaging.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 21 Sep 2017 07:45:56 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Provides the infrastructure for running and building daemons and services with Mono as well as various stub assemblies
